{"tid":1748295,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"一文分析區選及投票","createTime":"2019-11-23T15:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T16:46:15.000Z","uid":338636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"904a851079b2dd8bb1e1d459bcad4f49b1e8cb20","tid":1748295,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:10:36.000Z","msg":"又係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次歸納下區選投票同唔投嘅原因，至於投定唔投，就要交俾手機前嘅你自己決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>支持投票</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><strong>1）減少建制經濟來源</strong></ins></span></span><br />\n眾所周知，建制派因為薪金同政治獻金（中共），所以先可以有咁多人力物力，如果可以切斷佢其中一條米路（區選），就可以減少佢地嘅力量，例如係派刀手斬人、派啲廢老出嚟撕紙。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><strong>2）話俾世界聽民意冇逆轉又係我</strong></ins></span></span><br />\n全世界都十分注重今次嘅選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，因為建制贏咗就代表民意係佢地個邊，咁政府就可以大條道理話反對政府嘅人只係少數，唔需要理會，咁我地嘅說服力就有可能大減。所以唯有我地贏，先可以話俾全世界聽，香港人依然係好不滿政府，唔會相信保皇黨。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><strong>3）擴大小圈子入面黃嘅比例</strong></ins></span></span><br />\n好多人都好可能唔知，1200人嘅選舉小圈子入面，有117席係靠區議會互選出嚟，所以如果全個區議會都係泛民／本土，咁117席就一定係黃，會撐我地想揀嘅特首。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><strong>4）拒絕大白象工程</strong></ins></span></span><br />\n雖然話區議會冇實權，但偏偏佢有會過啲奇怪嘅議案，例如係5000萬音樂噴泉（民建聯潘進源）、630萬避雨亭（民建聯黃碧嬌）、全港最貴公園1.3億西樓角公園（民建聯黃偉傑）。仲有好多，無法詳列，但唔好唔記得呢啲垃圾、on9工程全部都係建制提出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而泛民係有嘗試阻止佢地通過，但因為唔夠人，最終大部分都係過晒。就算區議會係政治上冇用都好，係民生上都都係有用。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><strong>5）頂唔順條氣</strong></ins></span></span><br />\n呢個應該最易理解，如果俾你嘅敵人贏咗一仗，你都唔忿氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>支持白票</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><strong>1）制度內抗爭係冇用</strong></ins></span></span><br />\n而家嘅制度係政府定出嚟，而經過種種事件（DQ、冇權），我地已經認同咗制度係冇用，如果我地再參與係制度入面、再繼續投票，就係默認成個制度係正確，冇需要改變。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><strong>2）區議會冇實權</strong></ins></span></span><br />\n區議會只係諮詢機構，佢係唔會有任何權力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，就算贏咗都係冇用，同選立法會係唔同。而個啲大白象依舊可以係有功能組別嘅立法會度過。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><strong>3）建制資源無限</strong></ins></span></span><br />\n雖然區議會係建制其中一條米路，但建制真正嘅資金來源係中共，中共嘅資源係無限，所以你斷佢區選，中國或者政府一樣有源源不絕嘅錢俾佢地，就算你投邊個黨派結果都係唔會改變。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><strong>4）民意冇用</strong></ins></span></span><br />\n對而家極權嘅港共政府嚟講，民意只係垃圾。如果佢肯聽民意，二百萬個日佢就已經撤回咗送中法。所以結果係點都好，政府一樣係舞照跳、馬照跑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老實講，我係認同應該要投票嘅。雖然我係十分認同區議會本身真係冇撚用，但<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins><strong>若果要做到一齊杯葛選舉嘅效果，係有前提，就係一定要全部人都棄權</span></strong></ins></span>，但現況係我地有一班人想投票，已經做唔到全部人一齊唔投嘅效果。就算唔講我地本身啦，對面藍絲一樣係會投票，又點做到杯葛呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過如果你都係認為要投白票嘅話，我都會尊重你嘅選擇，因為我覺得只要目標都係想光復香港，咁無論你用咩手段，你都係手足（當然鬼同五毛除外）正如我上個po所講，贏嘅關鍵係不分化、不割蓆、不篤灰。<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><strong>但希望唔投票嘅話，你可以令到身邊嘅藍絲都杯葛個選舉，收埋將身份證又好，剪爛佢都好，咁先係真正實踐緊攬炒嘅理念。<br />\n<br />\n至於投票嘅你，記得一票不投保皇黨，優先揀本土，只後先係泛民。如果你個區有超過兩位泛民候選人，請你睇下連登同tg上面嘅巴打會揀邊個，同點解會咁揀。</strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>最後，兄弟爬山，各自努力。</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d589c788069784753a730604e79ca7ebd136a0a7","tid":1748295,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:11:31.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀，希望你地可以睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>一齊入嚟睇致勝關鍵！！！！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n[拒絕分化！]古人一早教我地點贏<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1739422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1739422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>全個連登都係負能量，我要你地有正能量啊</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c7e439260683269a6fdf07ff776b757c37e42123","tid":1748295,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:13:08.000Z","msg":"P牌冇人推，求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b17a910dbbff784ce5d92c95541e737d7df4251","tid":1748295,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:14:39.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72fa5beac0c5c5b1392f3bec8959b50486dde441","tid":1748295,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:17:46.000Z","msg":"唔記得咗講，無論聽日輸贏都好，區選都只係支線，請繼續抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5238c16f93477e7c33448e6ccfe67e1eb2e4dd7c","tid":1748295,"uid":47834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:36:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e7fa357bc0e903a9a40959ecc92e962858d5c64","tid":1748295,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:36:41.000Z","msg":"香城online玩家大型活動 投票Challenge<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9684c00a97dfc439017c2738cf5c5ca4f5e9d072","tid":1748295,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n投票踢走保皇黨 就係咁簡單"},{"pid":"83573b38b7a32c29cc918f22d1aa01afb54f552d","tid":1748295,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:46:15.000Z","msg":"[深度數據分析] 你知道嗎？多你一票好多<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezEboS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezEboS</a>"}]}